						               													<description>Hackagon is a cyber security game that can be played with 2-4 players. The game is about the challenge between the Blue Team and the Red Team.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The purpose of the game is to develop the best strategy to strengthen the security of the system or to deepen security gaps to create vulnerability in the system.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The factors for determining the winner of the game are created by individual or collective choices during the play and the right use of in-game elements.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The purpose of the Blue Team is to provide security of the current system. The Red Team aims at spreading in all cells of the system by doing the greatest harm to the system. The basic motivation of each team is the achievement of required basic information and their usage towards developing an effective strategy in accordance with the aim.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Besides, team members can behave as Purple Team during the play. Players who come to the relevant phase do interactive studies with each other to share data about cyber security vulnerabilities. The achievements in this part directly contribute to teams and players.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;All players in the game can earn extra income by actively taking place at cryptocurrency market. Players who experience market&amp;rsquo;s volatility based on the analysis and news on the relevant cards try to predict the investment tools to advantage them.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
